"Memory Piece Overview"
Memory Pieces shall be the standard for utilizing the properties of ⁠PSYCHE Energy (Soul) in the transfer ⁠Memories. They are these solid glowing tablets encased in one's physical ⁠Sentience, with a single panel that contains the physical memories from that soul. The panel slots into the casing akin to a puzzle block.
Its color is based on the originator's soul's natural frequency, making it straightforward and easy to identify what Pieces belonged to who.
> Court Note: Due to Khueen's detachment from mortal-kind, it is indeed not easy to identify who each memory piece belonged to. As such, take care and caution when utilizing memory pieces of unknown origin.

They can contain more than mere moments in time, some housing skills, traits, abilities, and even privileges.
Their capabilities are similar to a computer's Flash Drive storing data and programs, with these Memory Pieces being created specifically for more sentient entities, such as ⁠Humans, ⁠Alterants (Modified Humans), animals, even us ⁠Archkin.
> Court Note: In fact, the best way to obtain an Archkin's abilities is to acquire one of their memory pieces. Under any circumstance do NOT utilize a memory piece from an Archgod.
> All Archgodic memory pieces are to be offered up to The Vice President, lest they be confiscated by force.

"How to use Memory Pieces"
The process is simple, as I had to design it as such to where anyone can obtain the contents contained within a Memory Piece.
Simply smash the tablet onto your body. That is it.

As long as you have ⁠Sentience, the piece's Sentience Casing would detect the closest carrier of sentience— most likely being yourself.
After the piece shatters, it would turn into a dust similar to ⁠Archose, before rapidly invading your nearest oculus nerve, or eye.
> Court Note: This process may be is uncomfortable for first-time users. But the irritating feeing dissipates rather quickly. This is another oversight of Khueen's due to her lack of sympathy for mortals.

Should you be in a situation where you can't subject any kinetic energy onto the memory piece, simply rubbing it against your eye works just as effectively. It will shatter immediately and you'll obtain the piece's contents just the same.
> Court Note: This process has been verified to work more effectively than smashing the memory piece onto yourself... unfortunately.

"How to extract Memory Pieces"
